Luke Bryan's family gathered together over the weekend to celebrate a happy occasion. The couple's niece, Jordan Cheshire, married her longtime love, Clint Eudy, on Sunday (Sept. 5) in Tennessee.

#LukeandCarolineBryan #LukeBryan #LukeBryanNieceWedding

The country superstar's wife Caroline Bryan, his mom LeClaire, the wedding planner and more family and friends have been sharing pictures and well wishes on social media over the last week in the buildup to the wedding.

Jordan is the oldest of three children born to Bryan's older sister, Kelly, and her husband, Ben, who died within a seven-year span of each other.
